'''34united e-Sports Club''' was a Professional e-Sports Club was founded on October, 2010. This club ceased its activities in mid-2015.

== History ==
Founded in 2010, '''34united''' has become one of the most important Spanish e-Sports Club. Although they have Call of Duty and FIFA (formerly also CS:GO, ShootMania or even Halo 4) squads, their main team is the League of Legends one.

